[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":781},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2019\u002F12\u002F25\u002Fswitch-hexo-next-to-algolia-search\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2019\u002F12\u002F25\u002Fswitch-hexo-next-to-algolia-search\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2019\u002F12\u002F25\u002Fswitch-hexo-next-to-algolia-search\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2019\u002F12\u002F25\u002Fswitch-hexo-next-to-algolia-search\u002F":758,"related:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2019\u002F12\u002F25\u002Fswitch-hexo-next-to-algolia-search\u002F":767},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20191225\u002F2266233686\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":741,"date":742,"description":743,"extension":744,"lang":745,"meta":746,"navigation":747,"path":748,"readingMinutes":749,"seo":750,"standalone":751,"stem":752,"tags":753,"tldr":755,"updated":742,"url":756,"__hash__":757},"content\u002Fen\u002FHexo\u002Fswitch-hexo-next-to-algolia-search.md","Switching Hexo NexT to Algolia Search","6863326622",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":720},"minimark",[11,16,25,29,34,44,48,58,62,68,76,80,96,103,106,112,115,121,124,130,133,139,142,145,151,156,159,165,169,172,186,189,356,380,384,387,397,406,410,433,436,511,515,518,533,537,544,592,599,629,636,643,648,663,667,677,684,703,707,716],[12,13,15],"h2",{"id":14},"intro","Intro",[17,18,19,20,24],"p",{},"My posts have been getting bigger and ",[21,22,23],"code",{},"search.json"," along with them, so I'm switching to another search approach — Algolia.",[12,26,28],{"id":27},"environment","Environment",[30,31,33],"h3",{"id":32},"versions-environment","Versions & environment",[35,36,42],"pre",{"className":37,"code":39,"language":40,"meta":41},[38],"language-text","OS: Windows 10 X64\nNode.js: V11.7.0\nIDE: VS Code\n","text","",[21,43,39],{"__ignoreMap":41},[30,45,47],{"id":46},"hexo-version","Hexo version",[49,50,51,55],"ul",{},[52,53,54],"li",{},"hexo: 3.8.0",[52,56,57],{},"hexo-cli: 2.0.0",[12,59,61],{"id":60},"algolia","Algolia",[17,63,64,65,67],{},"As mentioned, with more posts, ",[21,66,23],{}," got pretty heavy (around 2.72 MB — looks small, but every search adds about a second of load). The whole search experience got slower, so I'm switching to a hosted search service. Writing this up because there don't seem to be many complete walkthroughs out there.",[17,69,70,71,75],{},"Algolia's free tier is actually really generous — 10,000 article records, 100,000 searches per month. More than enough for an average blogger (",[72,73,74],"del",{},"for me at least",").",[30,77,79],{"id":78},"sign-up","Sign up",[17,81,82,83,89,90,95],{},"Head to ",[84,85,60],"a",{"href":86,"rel":87},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.algolia.com\u002F",[88],"nofollow"," and ",[84,91,94],{"href":92,"rel":93},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.algolia.com\u002Fusers\u002Fsign_up",[88],"sign up"," (the button at the top looks like a power button). I just signed in with GitHub:",[17,97,98],{},[99,100],"img",{"alt":101,"src":102},"Sign in","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F2019-12-25_17-10-13.png",[17,104,105],{},"Fill in the info:",[17,107,108],{},[99,109],{"alt":110,"src":111},"Info","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F1577265178107.jpg",[17,113,114],{},"Pick a data centre — Hong Kong is fine as the default:",[17,116,117],{},[99,118],{"alt":119,"src":120},"Data centre","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F2019-12-25_16-42-25.png",[17,122,123],{},"Pick your project type (SaaS), and choose \"As soon as possible\" from the dropdown since you'll be using it shortly:",[17,125,126],{},[99,127],{"alt":128,"src":129},"SaaS","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F2019-12-25_17-23-35.png",[17,131,132],{},"Click \"Go to dashboard\":",[17,134,135],{},[99,136],{"alt":137,"src":138},"Go to dashboard","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F2019-12-25_17-24-19.png",[30,140,141],{"id":141},"dashboard",[17,143,144],{},"In the dashboard, it'll prompt you to \"Create Index\":",[17,146,147],{},[99,148],{"alt":149,"src":150},"Create Index","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F2019-12-25_17-28-03.png",[17,152,153],{},[99,154],{"alt":149,"src":155},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F2019-12-25_17-29-43.png",[17,157,158],{},"After creating the index, grab the API keys — copy \"Application ID\", \"Search-Only API Key\", and \"Admin API Key\":",[17,160,161],{},[99,162],{"alt":163,"src":164},"API Keys","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F1577266334891.jpg",[12,166,168],{"id":167},"install-hexo-algoliasearch","Install hexo-algoliasearch",[17,170,171],{},"Install the plugin:",[35,173,177],{"className":174,"code":175,"language":176,"meta":41,"style":41},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","npm install hexo-algoliasearch --save\n","cmd",[21,178,179],{"__ignoreMap":41},[180,181,184],"span",{"class":182,"line":183},"line",1,[180,185,175],{},[17,187,188],{},"Add this to Hexo's main config:",[35,190,194],{"className":191,"code":192,"language":193,"meta":41,"style":41},"language-yml shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","algolia:\n  appId: \"\" ## Application ID from above\n  applicationID: \"\" ## Application ID from above\n  apiKey: \"\" ## Search-Only API Key from above\n  adminApiKey: \"\" ## Admin API Key from above\n  chunkSize: 5000\n  indexName: \"isRayNotArray\"\n  fields:\n    - content:strip:truncate,0,500\n    - excerpt:strip\n    - gallery\n    - permalink\n    - photos\n    - slug\n    - tags\n    - title\n","yml",[21,195,196,205,222,234,247,260,272,283,291,300,308,316,324,332,340,348],{"__ignoreMap":41},[180,197,198,201],{"class":182,"line":183},[180,199,60],{"class":200},"sKpQp",[180,202,204],{"class":203},"sMAXC",":\n",[180,206,208,211,214,218],{"class":182,"line":207},2,[180,209,210],{"class":200},"  appId",[180,212,213],{"class":203},": ",[180,215,217],{"class":216},"sTRMh","\"\"",[180,219,221],{"class":220},"sQrFR"," ## Application ID from above\n",[180,223,225,228,230,232],{"class":182,"line":224},3,[180,226,227],{"class":200},"  applicationID",[180,229,213],{"class":203},[180,231,217],{"class":216},[180,233,221],{"class":220},[180,235,237,240,242,244],{"class":182,"line":236},4,[180,238,239],{"class":200},"  apiKey",[180,241,213],{"class":203},[180,243,217],{"class":216},[180,245,246],{"class":220}," ## Search-Only API Key from above\n",[180,248,250,253,255,257],{"class":182,"line":249},5,[180,251,252],{"class":200},"  adminApiKey",[180,254,213],{"class":203},[180,256,217],{"class":216},[180,258,259],{"class":220}," ## Admin API Key from above\n",[180,261,263,266,268],{"class":182,"line":262},6,[180,264,265],{"class":200},"  chunkSize",[180,267,213],{"class":203},[180,269,271],{"class":270},"sCcAr","5000\n",[180,273,275,278,280],{"class":182,"line":274},7,[180,276,277],{"class":200},"  indexName",[180,279,213],{"class":203},[180,281,282],{"class":216},"\"isRayNotArray\"\n",[180,284,286,289],{"class":182,"line":285},8,[180,287,288],{"class":200},"  fields",[180,290,204],{"class":203},[180,292,294,297],{"class":182,"line":293},9,[180,295,296],{"class":203},"    - ",[180,298,299],{"class":216},"content:strip:truncate,0,500\n",[180,301,303,305],{"class":182,"line":302},10,[180,304,296],{"class":203},[180,306,307],{"class":216},"excerpt:strip\n",[180,309,311,313],{"class":182,"line":310},11,[180,312,296],{"class":203},[180,314,315],{"class":216},"gallery\n",[180,317,319,321],{"class":182,"line":318},12,[180,320,296],{"class":203},[180,322,323],{"class":216},"permalink\n",[180,325,327,329],{"class":182,"line":326},13,[180,328,296],{"class":203},[180,330,331],{"class":216},"photos\n",[180,333,335,337],{"class":182,"line":334},14,[180,336,296],{"class":203},[180,338,339],{"class":216},"slug\n",[180,341,343,345],{"class":182,"line":342},15,[180,344,296],{"class":203},[180,346,347],{"class":216},"tags\n",[180,349,351,353],{"class":182,"line":350},16,[180,352,296],{"class":203},[180,354,355],{"class":216},"title\n",[17,357,358,359,89,362,365,366,369,370,372,373,376,377,379],{},"The reason ",[21,360,361],{},"appId",[21,363,364],{},"applicationID"," are both there is that NexT's bundled ",[21,367,368],{},"algolia-instant-search"," plugin reads ",[21,371,361],{},", while ",[21,374,375],{},"hexo-algoliasearch"," reads ",[21,378,364],{},". So you have to set both.",[12,381,383],{"id":382},"install-the-algolia-instant-search-extension","Install the algolia-instant-search extension",[17,385,386],{},"NexT needs an extension plugin too, otherwise Algolia won't work.",[17,388,389,392,393,396],{},[21,390,391],{},"cd"," into the theme folder (",[21,394,395],{},"cd theme\u002Fnext",") and run:",[35,398,400],{"className":174,"code":399,"language":176,"meta":41,"style":41},"git clone https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Ftheme-next\u002Ftheme-next-algolia-instant-search source\u002Flib\u002Falgolia-instant-search\n",[21,401,402],{"__ignoreMap":41},[180,403,404],{"class":182,"line":183},[180,405,399],{},[12,407,409],{"id":408},"enable-algolia-in-next-config","Enable Algolia in NexT config",[17,411,412,413,416,417,420,421,424,425,428,429,432],{},"Open the theme's ",[21,414,415],{},"_config.yml",", find ",[21,418,419],{},"algolia_search",", change ",[21,422,423],{},"false"," to ",[21,426,427],{},"true",". If ",[21,430,431],{},"Local search"," was previously enabled, disable it.",[17,434,435],{},"There are other knobs to tweak below. Mine looks like:",[35,437,439],{"className":191,"code":438,"language":193,"meta":41,"style":41},"algolia_search:\n  enable: true\n  hits:\n    per_page: 10\n  labels:\n    input_placeholder: Search posts & content\n    hits_empty: \"No results for: ${query}\"\n    hits_stats: \"Found ${hits} results in ${time} ms\"\n",[21,440,441,447,457,464,474,481,491,501],{"__ignoreMap":41},[180,442,443,445],{"class":182,"line":183},[180,444,419],{"class":200},[180,446,204],{"class":203},[180,448,449,452,454],{"class":182,"line":207},[180,450,451],{"class":200},"  enable",[180,453,213],{"class":203},[180,455,456],{"class":270},"true\n",[180,458,459,462],{"class":182,"line":224},[180,460,461],{"class":200},"  hits",[180,463,204],{"class":203},[180,465,466,469,471],{"class":182,"line":236},[180,467,468],{"class":200},"    per_page",[180,470,213],{"class":203},[180,472,473],{"class":270},"10\n",[180,475,476,479],{"class":182,"line":249},[180,477,478],{"class":200},"  labels",[180,480,204],{"class":203},[180,482,483,486,488],{"class":182,"line":262},[180,484,485],{"class":200},"    input_placeholder",[180,487,213],{"class":203},[180,489,490],{"class":216},"Search posts & content\n",[180,492,493,496,498],{"class":182,"line":274},[180,494,495],{"class":200},"    hits_empty",[180,497,213],{"class":203},[180,499,500],{"class":216},"\"No results for: ${query}\"\n",[180,502,503,506,508],{"class":182,"line":285},[180,504,505],{"class":200},"    hits_stats",[180,507,213],{"class":203},[180,509,510],{"class":216},"\"Found ${hits} results in ${time} ms\"\n",[12,512,514],{"id":513},"uploading-the-algolia-index","Uploading the Algolia index",[17,516,517],{},"Algolia doesn't auto-upload the index, so every time you update posts, you'll need to run:",[35,519,521],{"className":174,"code":520,"language":176,"meta":41,"style":41},"hexo clean\nhexo algolia\n",[21,522,523,528],{"__ignoreMap":41},[180,524,525],{"class":182,"line":183},[180,526,527],{},"hexo clean\n",[180,529,530],{"class":182,"line":207},[180,531,532],{},"hexo algolia\n",[12,534,536],{"id":535},"batch-script","Batch script",[17,538,539,540,543],{},"To make this less annoying, you can use a script. A ",[21,541,542],{},".bat"," example:",[35,545,549],{"className":546,"code":547,"language":548,"meta":41,"style":41},"language-js shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","@echo off\ncd 'D:\\WelcomeWebWorld' \u002F\u002F your blog project path\nhexo clean\nhexo generate\nhexo algolia\nhexo deploy\n","js",[21,550,551,556,574,578,583,587],{"__ignoreMap":41},[180,552,553],{"class":182,"line":183},[180,554,555],{"class":203},"@echo off\n",[180,557,558,561,564,568,571],{"class":182,"line":207},[180,559,560],{"class":203},"cd ",[180,562,563],{"class":216},"'D:",[180,565,567],{"class":566},"sWyjQ","\\W",[180,569,570],{"class":216},"elcomeWebWorld'",[180,572,573],{"class":220}," \u002F\u002F your blog project path\n",[180,575,576],{"class":182,"line":224},[180,577,527],{"class":203},[180,579,580],{"class":182,"line":236},[180,581,582],{"class":203},"hexo generate\n",[180,584,585],{"class":182,"line":249},[180,586,532],{"class":203},[180,588,589],{"class":182,"line":262},[180,590,591],{"class":203},"hexo deploy\n",[17,593,594,595,598],{},"Or, leveraging npm, add to ",[21,596,597],{},"package.json",":",[35,600,604],{"className":601,"code":602,"language":603,"meta":41,"style":41},"language-json shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","\"scripts\": {\n  \"start\": \"hexo clean && hexo generate && hexo algolia && hexo deploy\"\n},\n","json",[21,605,606,614,624],{"__ignoreMap":41},[180,607,608,611],{"class":182,"line":183},[180,609,610],{"class":216},"\"scripts\"",[180,612,613],{"class":203},": {\n",[180,615,616,619,621],{"class":182,"line":207},[180,617,618],{"class":200},"  \"start\"",[180,620,213],{"class":203},[180,622,623],{"class":216},"\"hexo clean && hexo generate && hexo algolia && hexo deploy\"\n",[180,625,626],{"class":182,"line":224},[180,627,628],{"class":203},"},\n",[17,630,631,632,635],{},"Then deploying Hexo is just ",[21,633,634],{},"npm start"," — runs everything in one go.",[30,637,639,642],{"id":638},"explained",[21,640,641],{},"&&"," explained",[17,644,645,646,598],{},"Quick note on ",[21,647,641],{},[49,649,650,657],{},[52,651,652,653,656],{},"A single ",[21,654,655],{},"&"," runs commands in parallel",[52,658,659,660,662],{},"A double ",[21,661,641],{}," runs them sequentially — the second only runs if the first succeeds",[12,664,666],{"id":665},"troubleshooting","Troubleshooting",[17,668,669,670,673,674,676],{},"If you hit ",[21,671,672],{},"algolia settings are invalid.",", possible causes: missing plugin install, didn't install the theme extension, or didn't add the right config to Hexo's ",[21,675,415],{},". Following the steps above should generally cover it.",[17,678,679,680,683],{},"One reminder: Algolia uses some pretty sensitive keys, so I'd recommend not making your blog source repo public, or encrypting the keys. The critical one is ",[21,681,682],{},"adminApiKey"," — don't share it.",[17,685,686,687,690,691,690,695,698,699,702],{},"Also: you have to run ",[21,688,689],{},"hexo generate"," ",[692,693,694],"em",{},"before",[21,696,697],{},"hexo algolia",", otherwise you'll keep seeing ",[21,700,701],{},"There is no post to index."," and the index won't update.",[12,704,706],{"id":705},"references","References",[49,708,709],{},[52,710,711],{},[84,712,715],{"href":713,"rel":714},"https:\u002F\u002Fchentging.github.io\u002F2018\u002F05\u002F16\u002Fhexo%EF%BC%9A%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89hexo-Next-%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-%E8%A1%A5%E5%85%85-Algolia-%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2\u002F",[88],"hexo: NexT theme — Algolia search (Chinese)",[717,718,719],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sKpQp, html code.shiki .sKpQp{--shiki-default:#72F088}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html pre.shiki code .sQrF